{
  "id": "expert-makeupf",
  "title": "makeupf",
  "description": "Create a 2D interactive makeup random matching system featuring a face mask setup and dynamic makeup component selection. The system includes a Makeup Controller that manages multiple makeup categories (contour, blush, eyebrows, eyelashes, eyeliner, eyeshadow, lipstick, and extras), randomly generating cohesive makeup combinations. It features carousel functionality with adjustable interval (0.1) and duration (2) for previewing makeup options, integrated with a face mask camera system for real-time application visualization. The system provides users with randomly matched makeup looks that can be previewed, selected, and applied to the face mask. [source: makeupf.json]",
  "gameType": "dress-up",
